headline: Baird Lowers its Price Target on Trimble Inc. (TRMB) to $90 but Maintains an Outperform Rating
summary: Trimble Inc. (NASDAQ:TRMB) is among the 10 Best Consensus Buy-Rated Stocks to Invest in. On February 11, 2026, Baird lowered its price target on Trimble Inc. (NASDAQ:TRMB) to $90 from $95 but still maintained an Outperform rating, updating its model after results that the firm said showed continued solid execution and initial 2026 guidance that […]
